INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('22797','姥爷的抗战','','laoyedekangzhan','L','','http://i2.letvimg.com/lc02_isvrs/201502/04/17/50/69048625-def6-487c-8683-0ee3fe0865b1.jpg','','','王学圻,蒋勤勤,李子雄,吕一,','蒋钦民,黄建勋,','英国留学,复仇者,火车站,八路军,地下党','正片','大陆','国语','0','12','','','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','470652','336857','611249','492650','0','0','0','6.0','0','311','1482141954','1482260818','0','0','姥爷是留日学习机械专业的优秀人才。9.18事变后，姥爷毅然回国接任了家族产业。循规蹈矩的姥爷与世无 争，但却因此被误认为是汉奸。当女儿携丈夫从英国留学归国，在火车站遭到鬼子强暴，孩子胎死腹中，女婿被鬼子打死时，忍气吞声的姥爷终于爆发，走上了向日军讨回血债的复仇之路。他利用高超的机械技术自制多种武器，与日方巧妙周旋，成为一名刺杀日军的神秘杀手。同时，姥爷还义无反顾地帮助八路军研制和改装炮弹，支持抗日。我地下党组织派遣策反他的人逐渐发现他的复仇秘密，国共双方联手准备帮助他时，姥爷的日方“知已”小岛、特高课杜松已将枪口对准了他。一场又一场惊心动魄的较量后，姥爷从一名单纯的个人复仇者，最终在谭丽萍和赵刚的协助和保护下成为抗日英雄战士。','letv','','','http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21388614.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21388735.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21393509.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21393548.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21395730.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21395790.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21399925.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21399930.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21395987.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21396046.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21396113.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21396149.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21400093.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21400486.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21400574.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21400667.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21400734.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437148.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437197.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437230.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437409.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437660.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437467.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437604.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437672.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437701.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437802.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21437682.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/21487510.html#http://